subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: What is the name of the oldest city in Rajasthan?
question_hi: राजस्थान में पहले से jayeकिस जिले का नाम है।
explanation_en: Udaipur is the oldest city in Rajasthan. It was founded in 1559 by Maharana Udai Singh II.
